{"tid":1691711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"｛更新｝向優品360同林子峰發出最後通諜2","createTime":"2019-11-03T18:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T23:16:45.000Z","uid":212624,"like":56,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"cb93ced7df1fd1274474d003c34a2f459a899b0b","tid":1691711,"uid":212624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:31:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原po</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n鑑於佢表明唔關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲話要捐身家 甘大家都講道理 要行動先有用 如果佢願意做齊以下呢幾樣野 手足可以考慮下降為裝飾同罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）立刻與所有撐警人士及企業割蓆<br />\n2）公開遣責811福建幫施襲者<br />\n3）辭去福建同鄉會榮譽主席<br />\n4）將佢三成股份套現 捐去612 星火<br />\n<br />\n大家都講道理嘅<br />\n<br />\n手足點睇 歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後大家對第四點有好強烈意見 反應兩極 有人話唔應該迫人捐錢 有人話三成太少 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我想澄清番一點 捐錢唔係我講 係佢講 不過我認我冇講清楚</span></strong><br />\n我知連仔唔爬文好懶 我送埋句野同條link比你又點話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>「若果你有證據話我同黑社會有關，我會捐咗優品360股份，冇做過怕乜？我捐晒成副身家都得」<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n不割席福建人 稱若證涉暴 林子峰：捐晒優品股票甚至百億身家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691164</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n於是我就整合左大家意見 整左份更新版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鑑於佢表明唔關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲話要捐身家 甘大家都講道理 要行動先有用 如果佢願意做齊以下呢幾樣野 手足可以考慮下降為裝飾同罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）立刻與所有撐警人士及企業割蓆<br />\n2）公開遣責811福建幫施襲者並供出相關人等<br />\n3）辭去福建同鄉會榮譽主席<br />\n4）公開為之前店鋪對示威者所做的失誤行為道歉<br />\n5）經大家調查發現林子峰及優品360的確與黑幫有關聯，上述一切內容立即失效，裝修繼續<br />\n大家都講道理嘅<br />\n<br />\n手足點睇 歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人會問 開呢條支線有咩意思 推番五大訴求相關<br />\n但我認為優品360始終都係商界一份子 仲要唔係小規模 我地而家係要爭取各方支持 特別係商界 我地要拉攏同團結我地嘅黃色經濟圈 甘樣對我地場運動同五大訴求 百利而無一害<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n歡迎百屌成材<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bd9cc8db3f9b85ffdc50bd0190cfb10faf8304","tid":1691711,"uid":212624,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:32:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新po</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n鑑於佢表明唔關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲話要捐身家 甘大家都講道理 要行動先有用 如果佢願意做齊以下呢幾樣野 手足可以考慮下降為裝飾同罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）立刻與所有撐警人士及企業割蓆<br />\n2）公開遣責811福建幫施襲者並供出相關人等<br />\n3）辭去福建同鄉會榮譽主席<br />\n4）公開為之前店鋪對示威者所做的失誤行為道歉<br />\n5）<strong>經大家調查發現林子峰及優品360的確與黑幫有關聯，上述一切內容立即失效，裝修繼續</strong><br />\n大家都講道理嘅<br />\n<br />\n手足點睇 歡迎討論"},{"pid":"cd1e990a7afe70bd3be206f16eb2eb7620f32ee0","tid":1691711,"uid":212624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:32:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c2362b423a636938e27808aeee09c68b46548f09","tid":1691711,"uid":212624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":